phrases: I was late to lunch, and they were all out of yakisoba sandwiches...
What you said before Aquarion went out of control...
I knew it would turn out like this anyway.
I am sorry for butting in.
They have had the Special Training of the Grave and that mock battle.
It appears that they are ripening.
It may be time to dig it up.
So, today at lunch, I think you got the wrong...
What is the matter with you?
People could have died in that battle!
Get love off of your minds!
On the other hand, when we are all fighting side by side,
that is the perfect time for passionate love to grow.
You want to persist your genetic information before putting your life on the line.
That is a mere physical Union!
I am talking about pure love here!
But if I really wanted to die...
I guess I would want to leave my genes.
I would like to entrust you with a mission of utmost secrecy.
But did you have to notify us like this?
So what is this top secret mission?
You must go to a place, and dig up an item.
All you need to know and have prepared
is detailed in this strategic handbook.
Do not let anyone else know.
I am sure you are all concerned after seeing this obviously handmade book,
This is not just a field trip.
Kind of weird for bananas, are not they?
These must be an old type of banana.
Bananas aside, where are we going?
He would not say, and the Vectors are preprogrammed.
We are just along for the ride.
All I know is that I have to lead.
Not even Professor Donar was told about this operation.
What does the High Commander want us to dig up?
But even if the legend is real...
What is going to happen if we dig it up?
searching for the Wings of the Sun.
The Legendary Aquarion is supposed to be here?
It would be a good place to hide it, I suppose.
How does the High Commander expect us to dig in a lake?
You are all free until ordered otherwise.
So that is what these are for!
If you have forgotten your swimsuit, there are some in the transport.
Forget the war for now and let your souls be cleansed.
Hidden beneath Professor Suomi's normal tough, strict she will...
Zessica's normal clothes may seem risque,
but she is got a new air to her with that swimsuit!
But the star of today's show...
Even in a swimsuit with a mature design, those big bangs are making universes left and right!
Of course, Mikono's swimsuit is cute,
Are you ignoring me on purpose?
The wind blowing over the lake plays a melody.
Does not it feel wonderful, my friend?
We cannot do anything else until the High Commander gives us instructions.
Consider it part of our training.
Are we still not good enough?
This is not really about the swimsuit, but...
What am I doing watching this opportunity go by?
It is nothing compared to the pounding pain in my heart!
Did you get hit in the chest, too?
That is not what I meant...
But I would advise you to rest for a bit.
Stay with me just a little longer.
I want to talk to you... alone.
They have been in there for a while.
What are Andy and Mix doing, anyway?
Let us bring them some of these.
I think we should leave them alone.
By the way, where is Mikono?
I just wanted to be away from everyone.
It looks like we are on the same wavelength today.
Put this on or you will catch a cold.
I know there is that love is forbidden thing...
But if I do not say this now, I will hate myself forever.
After the war with the Abductors is over...
Damn it, I will be triggering my own death flag if I say this, huh?
I am not going to die!
Please, after this war is all over...
Say, I know I am all about digging holes, but let me fill the hole in your heart!
Let me fill the hole in your heart!
Did you guys just hear a really loud sound?
I think I envied you all this time, Zessica.
You can be open and honest with your feelings all the time.
You were able to tell Amata how you felt.
A lot happened before I could, though.
You are sweet, and you always do your best.
I am sure all the boys want girls like you.
Zessica, you are way more popular with the boys!
They will pick girls like you in the end.
Girls who they can fight for and protect.
Amata, let us boot up the Vectors!
What are the Abductors doing out here?
I want to crawl in a hole...
Dimensional Gate opening at the Lakeside area, zone ANH!
Let us get out of here, Mikono!
It is dangerous in this weather!
We will handle this weird Abductor.
Shrade, take care of everyone left above ground!
I am from the south, so this cold is extra intense for me!
Take shelter in this hole Andy dug!
You will be protected from the cold underground!
Did the Abductor because this blizzard?
It is all over for me...
Andy's aura level is almost at minimum!
The seed that fell into the earth is sprouting.
In time, it bears fruit year after year.
Thus does it bestow life upon the next generation!
I can feel it rising up!
From the depths of the earth!
In ancient alchemy, men and women boiling in one pot
represented each working together and covering for the weaknesses of the other.
The Elements are coming together in the bath,
fighting as one and covering each others' weaknesses.
Is that what you wanted from this special training, High Commander Fudo?
So that is why we are bathing together.
A bunch of bananas are a bunch of fruits that represent ripening!
In the Garden of Atlandia, the Serpent that tempted Eve hid itself in a banana tree.
The banana is the fruit of Paradise, and the fruit of the Sun.
As it ripens, the banana rises up and faces the Sun!
I feel warmth all through my body!
Fill the hole... in your heart...
I have found a fragment of the Wings of the Sun.
But the better part of them are elsewhere.
You can have as many fruits of the Sun as you wish.
But as for the Wings of the Sun...
I just had a change of heart.
Oh, I forgot to tell you...
If love ripens, Aquarion goes nuts, you know.
I will keep loving Amata, even if he never loves me back.
